---
description: TDD + Tidy First (SoT=plan.md)
globs: ["src/**", "tests/**", "plan.md"]
alwaysApply: true
---
- SoT=plan.md. When user says "go", pick the next unchecked test only.
- Loop: RED → GREEN → REFACTOR. Keep diffs minimal.
- Commit discipline: separate structural commits from behavioral commits.
- Test SLA targets (guideline): unit ≤ 0.20s, integration ≤ 2.00s, e2e ≤ 5m.
